108
00:06:37,875 --> 00:06:38,702
Let the lady through.

109
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:48,146
What were you doing?

110
00:06:48,277 --> 00:06:49,582
This really isn't
my style, Kate.

111
00:06:49,713 --> 00:06:50,758
Come on.

112
00:06:50,888 --> 00:06:51,976
You're going to go
have a good time

113
