get paid for this.

116
00:07:27,359 --> 00:07:28,622
We just put this
dump on the map.

117
00:07:28,752 --> 00:07:29,623
Hey, Dominique.

118
00:07:29,753 --> 00:07:30,624
Care to dance?

119
