131
00:09:21,778 --> 00:09:23,388
KIM: Maybe you
should just lay off.

132
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:25,521
Oh if I need it, I'd take it.

133
00:09:25,652 --> 00:09:27,305
If I don't, I don't.

134
00:09:27,436 --> 00:09:29,960
You've been
drinking all night.

135
00:09:30,091 --> 00:09:33,790
