285
00:20:39,325 --> 00:20:41,936
Yes, I made my
business arrangements

286
00:20:42,066 --> 00:20:44,852
more quickly than I expected.

287
00:20:44,982 --> 00:20:48,856
The new club owner said
you were wonderful.

288
00:20:51,946 --> 00:20:52,729
I'm glad.

289
00:20:57,256 --> 00:21:01,782
